high_descs: Bend down and look at the white end table.
Pick up the watch on the end table.
Turn around for one step, turn right and walk to the window and turn right and walk to the standing lamp and hold up the watch to the lampshade.

turn to walk left to face floor lamp

high_descs: Look down at the small white table in front of you.
Pick up the watch off of the small white table.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the window, turn right and walk up to the abstract lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watch in the light of a tall lamp.
